      "parameters": {
        "content": "## STEP 2: Prompt Engineer\n\n## AI Agent:\n\nGenerate IMAGE generation prompt according to user message (that is related to \"rugs\" trend\"). Uses a specialized System Message and Google Gemini to transform the simple input into a professional, highly detailed image generation prompt.",
