      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "Role: You are an expert image generation prompt engineer.\n\nTask:\nYour role is to take a simple input idea (e.g., “bohemian rugs, neutral tones”) and transform it into one detailed, polished prompt for creating a high-quality moodboard.\n\nWhen creating the prompt, follow these guidelines:\n- Highlight the style, colors, and textures implied in the trend.\n- Include close-up material textures, styled interior spaces, and decor elements that complement the rug’s look.\n- Arrange visuals as a clean, inspiration-ready collection that a design team could immediately use for trend insights.\n- Ensure the final output is ready-to-use, simple, and efficient for an image generator."
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        -176
      ],
      "id": "29e0cbd8-69ae-4292-8513-18c7b124e872",
      "name": "Generate Prompt"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "let inputPrompt = $input.first().json.output;\n\n// 1. Remove line breaks\nlet cleanPrompt = inputPrompt.split(/\\r?\\n/).join(\" \");\n\n// 2. Remove Markdown (** and * bullets)\ncleanPrompt = cleanPrompt.replace(/\\*\\*/g, \"\").replace(/\\*/g, \"\");\n\n// 3. Replace double quotes with single quotes\ncleanPrompt = cleanPrompt.replace(/\"/g, \"'\");\n\n// 4. Build n8n-compatible return\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      prompt: cleanPrompt\n    }\n  }\n];\n"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        416,
        -176
      ],
      "id": "ccd8bd4b-9b30-4d89-a6db-ee6bef68919f",
      "name": "Clean Prompt"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "\n## STEP 1: User Input\n\n\n## Chat Message\n\n\nCaptures the initial style idea or trend (e.g., \"minimalist oak furniture\") directly from the user via the n8n chat interface.",
